Package com.pingidentity.sdk.provision.users.request

Interface ReadUsersRequestContext

  • All Superinterfaces:
    ProvisioningRequestContext
    public interface ReadUsersRequestContext
extends ProvisioningRequestContext
    An interface that represents the request context for a read users operation. It contains all the information needed to fulfill the request, e.g. filter.
    Since:
    8.0
